snippet.title: Brix gameplay (PC Game, 1991)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Brix, Dos PC game produced by Epic Megagames in 1991 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/brix/138/
Playing through a few levels of this clever and addictive little puzzler.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
